== INSTALL ==

cmake:
    $ make
    $ mv tower /your/favourite/path/bin
    $ tower

Windows:
    install a compiler: https://releases.llvm.org/download.html
    NOTE: make sure to select 'Add LLVM to the system PATH' option during installation
    > cd %HOMEPATH%\Downloads\the_tower
    > clang++ *.cpp -o tower.exe
    > tower.exe
